These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, tea
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, blues, funk
1. the fan of blues is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking tea is between the fan of funk and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
3. the person drinking cola is on the right of the fan of electronic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | tea | cola |
| Music-Genre   | blues     | electronic    | funk   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: woodworking, card-games, collecting
The people have 3 different jobs:  scientist, dancer, electrician
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the electrician is between the scientist and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Hobby   | woodworking    | collecting        | card-games |
| Job     | dancer | electrician | scientist         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, lemonade, coffee
3 different pets are kept: cat, frog, goat
1. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is between the owner of the frog and the person drinking coffee##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Beverage   | lemonade | soy-milk     | coffee |
| Pet        | frog  | goat | cat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, hip-hop, house
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, lizard, chinchilla
1. the fan of blues is the owner of the rabbit##1
2. the fan of house is between the owner of the lizard and the owner of the rabbit##2
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | house     | blues |
| Pet           | lizard | chinchilla | rabbit |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: singing, birding, rock-climbing
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, bird, frog
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the owner of the frog and the owner of the bird##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Hobby   | birding | rock-climbing     | singing |
| Pet     | frog    | guinea-pig | bird    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: french, german, canadian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, volleyball, tennis
1. the person who's sport is skiing is between the canadian and the french##2
2. the french is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
3. the german is on the right of the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Nationality   | french  | german   | canadian        |
| Sport         | volleyball | skiing | tennis |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: apricot, strawberry, artichoke
There are 3 different nationalities: german, malaysian, french
1. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
2. the german is between the person eating artichoke and the malaysian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | strawberry  | apricot  | artichoke |
| Nationality   | malaysian | german | french     |

