.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: thriller, epic, spy
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, chinese, american
1. the person watching epic movies is the american##1
2. the chinese is between the person watching epic movies and the person watching spy movies##2
3. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | spy   | thriller  | epic  |
| Nationality   | indonesian | chinese | american |

