.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, handball, badminton
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, van, skateboard
1. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
2. the person driving the trike is between the person who's sport is badminton and the person driving the van##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Sport       | badminton | parkour | handball  |
| Transport   | skateboard    | trike        | van |

