.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, milk, coffee
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, rock, indie
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking milk is between the person drinking coffee and the fan of rock##2
3. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Beverage      | coffee | milk   | almond-milk |
| Music-Genre   | indie  | d&b | rock   |

 